                                <div class="h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-8 border-white bg-primary ring-1 ring-gray-400/70 dark:border-darker dark:bg-white dark:ring-gray-700"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="">
                                <span class="text-gray-500">2021</span>
                                <h3 class="mt-0.5 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Startup of the year</h3>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Asperiores nemo possimus nesciunt dicta veniam aspernatur quam mollitia</p>
